{"tid":204821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【得罪習總】串錯國家名咁大鑊！ 中國導遊資格證書回收重印","createTime":"2017-04-17T10:51:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T15:51:43.000Z","uid":22675,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8c4e20b52819430feeb5c587dcd9728fe74b4d2c","tid":204821,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T10:51:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170417/large/1492420888_fde3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170417%2Flarge%2F1492420888_fde3.jpg&h=62c99d50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大件事！國家旅遊局近日發出通知，剛發放的2016年「導遊資格證書」，因印刷錯誤需要重新印製，要求導遊盡快將已發出的證書退回協會。根據網上圖片顯示，證書將中華人民共和國的英文「The People's Republic of China」印少了「The」，又把「Republic」串成「Republie」。<br />\n<br />\n江蘇南京導遊王先生稱，自己是去年參加全國導遊資格證考試，今年順利取得證書。本來是一件很開心的事情，他拿到手的時候也挺高興，但很快就發覺不太對勁，拿出舊導遊證書比對，發現新證書封面上的「Republic」，竟然拼寫成「Republie」。<br />\n另一位名導遊張女士也說：「當時沒太在意，後來相繼接到一批考試的同行和考生發來短訊，說證件封皮好像不太對。後經仔細查看，下發的導遊資格證鬧出了『笑話』，封皮正上方的共和國英語出現印刷錯誤，正確拼寫應為『Republic』，但我拿到的卻是『Republie』。」<br />\n事件在微信朋友圈熱傳，不少導遊奇怪怎麼導遊資格證書會出現這種「低級錯誤」。有導遊表示，後來才知道，去年這一批考試的學員拿到的導遊資格證書，在全國多地均出現了錯誤；故有不少導遊獲知後，戲稱自己拿到了假證書。<br />\n《金陵晚報》  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170417/56575844\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170417%2F56575844&d=9MYRmPDtC2YjWedq%2F%2FxxgcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=04701d46\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170417%2F56575844&h=22ed66ab\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170417/56575844</a>"},{"pid":"8cfe2d6644dcf548bb217abd03cada9d9d3fbd05","tid":204821,"uid":5253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T10:54:31.000Z","msg":"強國政府捉假證件新策略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n寫岩=假證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6a60e7ceaffc238d6e0f00092769948c8725ce9","tid":204821,"uid":2155,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T11:11:59.000Z","msg":"柒到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3696aa141f14c8f47333f95de3d17e789395469","tid":204821,"uid":62950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T11:14:34.000Z","msg":"真旅遊局 出 錯既證件<br />\n<br />\n偽造反而可能出到串岩既證件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1364602c633884b7eb99896f382c5476295ddc3","tid":204821,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T11:15:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>強國政府捉假證件新策略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n寫岩=假證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n柒左就柒左"},{"pid":"8cc86fc9222316e03ad7dd2460766750038a757b","tid":204821,"uid":5253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T11:26:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>強國政府捉假證件新策略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n寫岩=假證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n柒左就柒左</blockquote><br />\nWOW你好醒"},{"pid":"25ff67126318a766cacbc3f99cd48949673889b5","tid":204821,"uid":39174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T11:28:29.000Z","msg":"假的有時比真的好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dd33bb8abfb241023eef0aaea522c77af51fae3","tid":204821,"uid":7125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T11:59:58.000Z","msg":"串岩既反而假證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家啞樣防偽"},{"pid":"5c840c893ab7ec5a5a35955c80685334c01b30ed","tid":204821,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"